('9', 'Macross FB7: Ginga Rukon - Ore no Uta wo Kike!', 'In 2059, five decades after the Space War I conflict seen in the first Macross story. Macross Frontier, the 25th New Macross Class super-long-distance colonization fleet, is journeying through the galaxy to a new paradise to call home. However, it is locked in a state of war with a strange enemy called Vajra.<br><br>\r\nMacross FB7 is the 30th anniversary work of the Macross franchise.', 'FINISHED', '62', '2018-10-07 12:14:42', '2018-10-07 12:14:42', 'Ozma Meets Fire Bomber Macross FB7', 'マクロスFB7 銀河流魂 オレノウタヲキケ!', NULL, 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/reg/15177.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/med/15177.jpg'),
