('20', 'Smile Precure! Movie: Ehon no Naka wa Minna Chiguhagu!', 'The movie transports the Precure into a world inside a picture book, where they are guided by Nico, a mysterious inhabitant of the picture book world.', 'FINISHED', '72', '2018-10-07 12:19:25', '2018-10-07 12:19:25', NULL, '映画 スマイルプリキュア! 絵本の中はみんなチグハグ!', NULL, 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/reg/15307.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/med/15307.jpg'),
