('141', 'Zettai Karen Children: The Unlimited - Hyoubu Kyousuke', 'You don’t have to be psychic to know that Hyoubu Kyousuke is trouble waiting to happen, but having psychic powers of your own may be your only chance if you want to stand against him.  One of the most powerful espers on the planet, Hyoubu\'s incredible range of abilities extends as far as controlling his own aging process, and the potential strength of all his talents combined is so terrifying that he wears a device that limits their use except in cases of extreme emergency.  The time is coming, however, when Hyoubu will need to unleash everything he has.  Because sometimes it takes a villain to do what heroes can’t, and as the leader of the secret organization PANDRA, Hyoubu\'s dedicated his life to fighting those who would entrap, enslave, or kill anyone with psychic powers.  Now PANDRA itself is in danger and, to combat that deadly threat, the gloves and limiter are coming off!<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Sentai Filmworks)', 'FINISHED', '73', '2018-10-07 12:45:16', '2018-10-07 12:45:16', 'Unlimited Psychic Squad', '絶対可憐チルドレン THE UNLIMITED 兵部京介', NULL, 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/reg/16005.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/med/16005.jpg'),
