('169', 'Marriage Blue', 'This is a story about Sayaka and Masaharu, college juniors, who are about to get married together. Everyone knows Sayaka to be a conservative woman and is saving sex for after marriage. However, Kaneko-senpai, considered to be a reliable senior by Masaharu, has other plans to change Kudou’s mindset. He finally gets his chance after Masaharu cancels due to work and he takes it.\n<br><br>\nWill Kaneko succeed in his evil deeds to turn Kudou Sayaka from a conservative woman into a horny slut?', 'FINISHED', '55', '2018-10-07 12:52:16', '2018-10-07 12:52:16', NULL, 'マリッジブルー', NULL, 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/reg/16187.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/med/16187.jpg'),
