('172', 'Aku no Hana', 'Kasuga Takao is a boy who loves reading books, particularly Baudelaire\'s Les Fleurs du Mal. A girl at his school, Saeki Nanako, is his muse and his Venus, and he admires her from a distance. One day, he forgets his copy of Les Fleurs du Mal in the classroom and runs back alone to pick it up. In the classroom, he finds not only his book, but Saeki\'s gym uniform. On a mad impulse, he steals it.<br><br>\nNow everyone knows \"some pervert\" stole Saeki\'s uniform, and Kasuga is dying with shame and guilt. Furthermore, the weird, creepy, and friendless girl of the class, Nakamura, saw him take the uniform. Instead of revealing it was him, she recognizes his kindred deviant spirit and uses her knowledge to take control of his life. Will it be possible for Kasuga to get closer to Saeki, despite Nakamura\'s meddling and his dark secret? What exactly does Nakamura intend to do with him?<br><br>\n(Source: MangaHelpers)', 'FINISHED', '64', '2018-10-07 12:52:48', '2018-10-07 12:52:48', 'Flowers of Evil', '惡の華', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/banner/16201-64JGqbNltJhq.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/reg/16201.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/med/16201.jpg'),
('173', 'Bakumatsu Gijinden Roman', 'The stage is the close of the Edo period, an age when, not unlike our own time, both natural and man-made disasters left chaos in their wake. Manjiro makes a living helping the people of the troubled capital city, but behind the scenes, he also works in secret to take back precious belongings stolen from the people by unjust political powers and conspiratorial menaces. The people call him \"Get-backer Roman.\"<br><br>\n(Source: Crunchyroll)', 'FINISHED', '57', '2018-10-07 12:53:11', '2018-10-07 12:53:11', 'Bakumatsu Gijinden Roman', '幕末義人伝 浪漫', NULL, 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/reg/16211.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/med/16211.jpg'),
