('221', 'Soushisouai Note: The Animation', 'Based on the manga by Fukudahda.<br>\n<br>\nPart 1: Ashoka Madoka is invited to karaoke with his friends where he is introduced to Miyamoto who by chance they know each other from before. Two other girls went with two other boys. Later, Madoka and Miyamoto come out of the karaoke, hire a love hotel, and do a pervert thing.<br>\n<br>\nPart 2: Ai-chan is a girl who likes the smell of Namikawa sweat and she is starting to like Namikawa. After school, they go to the school warehouse and they both do a pervert things.<br>\n<br>\n(Source: Nekopoi and has been translated and also edited a bit from the original)', 'FINISHED', '67', '2018-10-07 13:03:30', '2018-10-07 13:03:30', NULL, '相思相愛ノート THE ANIMATION', NULL, 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/reg/16474.jpg', 'https://cdn.anilist.co/img/dir/anime/med/16474.jpg'),
